imized laws\nlearned for one regime performs well for the other untested regime as well. The\nproposed control strategy can be expected to be applicable for many other shear\nflow experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Feb 2022 16:54:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 13:08:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
