ulent mixing, but at the\ncost that other stellar parameters cannot be reproduced simultaneously. The\ndifficulty to reproduce the k2-value simultaneously with the stellar parameters\nas well as the incompatibility between the age estimates of the primary and\nsecondary stars are indications that some physics of the stellar interior are\nstill not completely understood.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2022 08:15:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-27"}
